4 A BILL FOR AN ACT ENTITLED: “AN ACT PROVIDING FOR NUTRIENT POLLUTANT LOADING OFFSETS,
5 OFFSET AMOUNTS, AND TRADING CREDITS FOR WATER QUALITY DISCHARGE PERMITS; PROVIDING
6 RULEMAKING AUTHORITY; AND PROVIDING AN IMMEDIATE EFFECTIVE DATE.”
